---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Home"
  description="Eoin McAllister is an ML engineer building reinforcement learning systems, research prototypes, and production ML infrastructure."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Eoin McAllister</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">ML engineer working on reinforcement learning, evaluation, and production ML systems.</h1>
    <p class="hero-lead">
      This site is a straightforward overview of my work. The fastest path is:
      read a project, inspect the code, then use the research and about pages for context.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/projects" class="btn-primary">View projects</a>
      <a href="/research" class="btn-ghost">Research</a>
      <a href="/about" class="btn-ghost">About me</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="summary">
    <div class="summary-item">
      <span class="summary-label">Current focus</span>
      <p>Language-conditioned control for RL agents without task-specific retraining.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-item">
      <span class="summary-label">Background</span>
      <p>Based in Dublin. Previously Intel. Currently building at UrbanFox.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-item">
      <span class="summary-label">Typical work</span>
      <p>RL experiments, evaluation tooling, shared infrastructure, and production ML systems.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section featured">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="section-kicker">Selected project</p>
      <h2>One concrete example.</h2>
    </div>

    <a href="/projects/control-console" class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-main">
        <span class="card-tag">Dummy project</span>
        <h3>Control Console for RL Experiments</h3>
        <p>
          A placeholder case study for testing the portfolio structure. It represents the kind of
          project page I want here: problem, architecture, implementation details, and evaluation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-meta">
        <span>Python</span>
        <span>FastAPI</span>
        <span>Postgres</span>
        <span>Experiment tracking</span>
      </div>
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <p class="section-kicker">Start here</p>
      <h2>How to read the site.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="cards">
      <a href="/projects" class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Projects</span>
        <h3>Code and case studies</h3>
        <p>Use this first if you want to see implementation choices, tooling, and concrete outputs.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/research" class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">Research</span>
        <h3>Technical interests</h3>
        <p>Use this to see the RL questions I am working on and the kinds of systems problems I care about.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/about" class="card">
        <span class="card-tag">About</span>
        <h3>Background</h3>
        <p>Use this for quick context on experience, focus areas, and where I have worked.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: var(--space-section) var(--space-page) 52px;
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .eyebrow,
  .section-kicker,
  .summary-label,
  .card-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-faint);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 58px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    max-width: 780px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .hero-lead {
    max-width: 620px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary,
  .btn-ghost {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-text);
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    border: 0.5px solid var(--color-border-mid);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .summary,
  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .summary {
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .summary-item,
  .card,
  .feature-card {
    padding: 24px var(--space-page);
  }

  .summary-item,
  .card {
    border-right: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .summary-item:last-child,
  .card:last-child {
    border-right: none;
  }

  .summary-item p,
  .card p,
  .feature-card p {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 52px 0 0;
  }

  .section-heading {
    padding: 0 var(--space-page) 22px;
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  .section-heading h2 {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .cards {
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .card {
    display: block;
    transition: background 0.12s ease;
  }

  .feature-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.8fr) minmax(220px, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
    color: inherit;
    transition: background 0.12s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    background: rgba(128, 128, 120, 0.04);
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    background: rgba(128, 128, 120, 0.04);
  }

  .card h3,
  .feature-card h3 {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .feature-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-content: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .feature-meta span {
    border: 0.5px solid var(--color-border-mid);
    padding: 5px 9px;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-faint);
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .summary,
    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .summary-item,
    .card {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .summary .summary-item:last-child,
    .cards .card:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .feature-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
